These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, romance, action, documentary
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, rugby, tennis
1. the person watching action movies is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is rowing##2
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
3. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
4. the person who's sport is rowing is not the person watching action movies##6
5. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5
6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary  | musical | action | romance  |
| Sport   | biathlon | rugby   | tennis  | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, pink, purple, black
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, journalist, nurse, project-manager
1. the project-manager is not to the left of the project-manager##8
2. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the right of the person who likes black##5
3. the person who likes mauve is the journalist##1
4. the person who likes black is between the person who likes mauve and the person who likes pink##2
5. the person who likes pink is somewhere between the person who likes purple and the designer##7
6. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the person who likes pink##5
7. the designer is not to the left of the designer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Color   | purple | pink          | black | mauve     |
| Job    | nurse      | project-manager | designer | journalist |

