.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, electrician, nurse, paramedic
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, may, june, august
1. the person who's birthday is in november is not to the left of the nurse##8
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
3. the electrician is on the right of the bartender##1
4. the electrician is in an even position##4
5. the paramedic is on the far left or far right##3
6. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##5
7. the paramedic is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | bartender | electrician | nurse     | paramedic |
| Birthday   | may    | august   | november | june    |

