.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, snooker, billiard, poker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
4. the person playing poker is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
5. the person playing monopoly is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Game   | billiard   | snooker         | poker   | monopoly    |
| Sport         | parkour | weightlifting | soccer | lacrosse |

