.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, family, romance, scientific
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, trance, salsa, reggae
1. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching epic movies and the person watching family movies##7
2. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the fan of salsa##5
3. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching romance movies and the person watching epic movies##7
4. the person watching romance movies is not to the left of the fan of reggae##8
5. the fan of reggae is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the fan of trance##7
6. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person watching scientific movies##5
7. the fan of trance is not to the left of the person watching epic movies##8
8. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | family   | romance | scientific | epic    |
| Music-Genre         | funk | reggae   | salsa   | trance |

