.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, kiwi, lettuce, pineapple
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, brown, yellow, light-blue
1. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
2. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the left of the person eating cauliflower##5
3. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
4. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
5. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
6. the person eating pineapple is not to the left of the person who likes brown##8
7. the person eating pineapple is the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | pineapple | cauliflower | kiwi  | lettuce |
| Color   | brown   | light-blue         | yellow | ivory |

