.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, sprite, water
City: san-francisco, london, venice, miami
1. the person traveling to london is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
2. the person traveling to miami is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person traveling to venice##7
3. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
4. the person traveling to miami is not to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##8
5. the person traveling to miami is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
7. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | cola      | sprite | almond-milk | water   |
| City      | san-francisco | venice | miami  | london |

