1. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
2. the indian is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5
3. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##5
4. the person who's birthday is in august is not to the right of the japanese##8
5. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the left of the indian##8
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3    |   4    |
| Nationality   | dutch     | japanese | indian | german |
| Birthday     | june | august  | december    | july   |

