.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, lime, onion, pineapple
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, aquamarine, blood-red, light-blue
1. the person eating onion is not to the right of the person who likes light-blue##8
2. the person who likes emerald is not to the right of the person eating lime##8
3. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the right of the person eating pineapple##5
4. the person who likes emerald is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating onion is between the person who likes light-blue and the person who likes blood-red##2
6. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
7. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | lime        | pineapple | onion      | corn    |
| Color   | emerald | blood-red   | aquamarine | light-blue |

