.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, papaya, watermelon, zucchini
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, amaryllis, bellflower, poppy
 1. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbellflower##5
 2. the person eating zucchini is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
 3. the person eating grapefruit is the person who growsbellflower##1
 4. the person who growsbellflower is not to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##8
 5. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 6. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the person who growsbellflower##8
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is not to the left of the person eating grapefruit##8
10. the person eating papaya is not to the left of the person who growstulip##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | papaya    | watermelon | grapefruit | zucchini |
| Flower   | tulip | poppy  | bellflower     | amaryllis    |

