.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, avocado, grapefruit, peas
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, ship, scooter, skateboard
1. the person eating grapefruit is the person driving the van##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
3. the person driving the ship is the person driving the ship##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is the person eating peas##1
5. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
6. the person eating avocado is between the person driving the ship and the person eating peas##2
7. the person eating grapefruit is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food    | peas        | avocado | asparagus | grapefruit |
| Transport   | skateboard | scooter | ship   | van    |

