.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, hamster, hedgehog
There 4 different types of food: orange, eggplant, banana, asparagus
1. the person eating eggplant is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
2. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the person eating asparagus##8
4. the owner of the hamster is the person eating orange##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the person eating eggplant and the person eating orange##7
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person eating banana is between the person eating asparagus and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | frog    | hedgehog | chinchilla | hamster |
| Food   | eggplant | asparagus      | banana     | orange     |

 